<h3 id="colors">Colors</h3>

<p>The border spinner uses <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">currentColor</code> for its <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">border-color</code>, meaning you can customize the color with <a href="/html-homeid/docs//utilities/colors/">text color utilities</a>. You can use any of our text color utilities on the standard spinner.</p>

