<h3 id="placement">Placement</h3>

<p>Use <a href="/html-homeid/docs//utilities/flex/">flexbox utilities</a>, <a href="/html-homeid/docs//utilities/float/">float utilities</a>, or <a href="/html-homeid/docs//content/typography/">text alignment</a> utilities to place spinners exactly where you need them in any situation.</p>

