<h2 id="size">Size</h2>

<p>Add <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.spinner-border-sm</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.spinner-grow-sm</code> to make a smaller spinner that can quickly be used within other components.</p>

<div class="bd-example-wrapper">
    <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <a class="nav-link active" data-toggle="tab" href="#result-322" role="tab" aria-controls="result-322" aria-selected="true">Result</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#html-322" role="tab" aria-controls="html-322" aria-selected="false">HTML Code</a>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="tab-content" id="examplte-tab-content-322">
